select `metanames`.`id`, `metanames`.`metaname_name` from `metanames` inner join `qns_appliedtos` on `qns_appliedtos`.`metaname_id` = `metanames`.`id` where `qns_appliedtos`.`department_id` = 5 group by `metanames`.`id`
select count(*) as aggregate from `assets` where `assets`.`metaname_id` = 1 and `assets`.`property_id` = 1
select `assets`.`id`, `assets`.`metaname_id`, `assets`.`asset_name`, `assets`.`property_id` from `assets` where `assets`.`metaname_id` = 1 and `assets`.`property_id` = 1 limit 8 offset 32

select `roles`.*, `model_has_roles`.`model_id` as `pivot_model_id`, `model_has_roles`.`role_id` as `pivot_role_id`, `model_has_roles`.`model_type` as `pivot_model_type` from `roles` inner join `model_has_roles` on `roles`.`id` = `model_has_roles`.`role_id` where `model_has_roles`.`model_id` in (11) and `model_has_roles`.`model_type` = 'App\Models\User'
